{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 213.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I came back, I start thinking about my, my demobilization because eventually, they would have demobilized me and sent me back to Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a very big concern to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I felt that's not, not my goal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Plus the fact-- there was something also interesting which I have to mention.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is something that I, I feel very rewarded that I was able to, to, in a certain way, to, to get some vengeance, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was that the Russian government has decided to transplant some factories-- the IG Farben factory and some other factories-- to take them from Berlin and take them over to Russia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the idea was to take the, the whole factory, all the machinery, with the workers, and the scientists, and the engineers, and everybody else.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was-- I received a, a, a letter which I, I was-- I was told I cannot open up this letter at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was, like, 21 hours, which was 9 o'clock in the-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the letter stated that I have, to my disposal, a truck with six soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I have to visit-- they gave me a map-- and to visit certain streets and to take in Germans who work for the IG Farben in order to take them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That should be-- I should start doing that at 12 o'clock midnight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by 4 o'clock in the morning, I should be finished with, with, with my task.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so-- and so did some other officers have done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this was really rewarding because I used to come and knock on the door of the German and used to tell them, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And get, get your luggage and your baggage.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
